</RulesElement>

<RulesElement name="Critical Sacrifice" type="Feat" internal-id="ID_TIV_FEAT_9000_03" source="Critical Augmentation Feats" revision-date="00/00/0000 00:00:00 PM">
    <Flavor> Your foe falls to the floor, from the massive blow you dealt it. The warmth of its blood on your hands revitalizes you. </Flavor>
    <specific name="Tier"> Heroic </specific>
    <specific name="Short Description"> Regain hit points as if you had spent a healing surge when you score a critical hit on your enemy and reduce it to 0 hit points. </specific>
    <specific name="Special"/>
    <specific name="type"> Critical Augmentation </specific>
    <specific name="Associated Power Info"/>
    <specific name="Associated Powers"/>
When you score a critical hit which reduces a creature to 0 hit points, you regain hit points as though you had spent a healing surge.
</RulesElement>

