<RulesElement name="Hounding Critical" type="Feat" internal-id="ID_TIV_FEAT_9000_25" source="Critical Augmentation Feats" revision-date="00/00/0000 00:00:00 PM">
    <Flavor> You catch your foe offguard, you easily slice your blade through its hindquarters, crippling it. </Flavor>
    <specific name="Tier"> Heroic </specific>
    <specific name="Short Description"> When you score a critical hit, against your marked target it takes an additional -2 penalty to attack rolls with attacks that do not include you as a target until it is no longer marked by you.</specific>
    <specific name="Special"/>
    <specific name="type"> Critical Augmentation </specific>
    <specific name="Associated Power Info"/>
    <specific name="Associated Powers"/> 
When you score a critical hit against a creature that is marked by you, or when you mark a creature that you scored a critical hit against since the end of your last turn, the target of your attack takes an additional -2 penalty to attack rolls with attacks that do not include you as a target until it is no longer marked by you.
</RulesElement>

